personally, I'm just looking for a reason.<br>
Maybe, if it's a good reason, Saga might adopt it.<br>
I understand if a guild says &quot;No evils&quot;. I understand if a guild says &quot;Group with Anyone.&quot; I do not understand &quot;only 1 but not 2.&quot;<br>
